title: MBMBaM 331: Bro's Better, Bro's Best Ch. 112-121
description: Well, now Griffin had a baby too. Listen, we've heard all the jokes already, so let us just save you some time: The McElroy Brothers can't stop procreating. We get it. Ha-ha. Anyway, here's another greatest hits episode, we hope you like it half as much as we like MAKING BABIES.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
